name: Dustin Dark
text: Most dishonest and unprofessional job I've ever had. Getting paid for hours worked so like po pulling teeth. They've TRIED to short me over a grand in the last 6 months of employment. Then fired me for points without following procedure while newer employees have more points but kept job. Not to mention firing me a week before my vacation and refusing to give me  that money.

name: cindy hauboldt
text: Nice people, but management was not very nice, backstabbing, and only had 1 month to prove myself, which to me is unrealistic expectation. Its a brand new start up facility with lots of challenges, work to be done, and processes to be implemented. Its to bad that the people I had to report to were not realistic of my potential for them. They also told me one thing about me being let go and I found out from the recruiting company the real reason that my boss gave them. They gave me NO WARNING, which has left me and my life a mess. They also were messing with my unemployment verifying. I am in a very sad situation now, cant' find a job and I also think I am black-balled from them.  THIS IS A WARNING to those that think its a good company.

name: Mrs. Laura Lewis
text: The manager, Maryanne is very unprofessional and rude. She could also use some diversity training. She will not last! Respect is earned not demanded!
